title: A History of American Tank Anthology by R.P.Hunnicutt
description:
A HISTORY OF AMERICAN TANK ANTHOLOGY
by R.P.HUNNICUTT

This torrent contains the following titles (in alphabetical order)

1. Abrams: A History of the American Main Battle Tank (Volume 2)
2. Firepower: A History of the American Heavy Tank
3. Patton: A History of the American Main Battle Tank   
4. Pershing: A History of the Medium Tank T20 Series
5. Sheridan: A History of the American Light Tank (Volume 2)
6. Sherman: A History of the American Medium Tank 
7. Stuart: A History of the American Light Tank 

DESCRIPTION:
The most comprehensive history of American tanks from Mk VIII to M1 Abrams. All titles contain black and white photographs and cover the various types in exhaustive detail. Ideal for modelers and students of armored warfare.
